# Testing Rules

## Visual Debugging
- Include visual feedback for transformations
- Add toggles for debug visualization
- Visualize coordinate systems and reference points

## Test at Multiple Levels
- Test individual transform components
- Test transform composition
- Test complete rendering pipeline
- Verify no information loss between steps

## Test Edge Cases
- Test extreme transform values
- Verify behavior with shift/modifier keys
- Test interaction between different transform types

## Visual Regression Testing
- Maintain visual regression test suite
- Document expected visual outcomes
- Test across different screen sizes and DPI settings 